title: Popcorn Time (Beta 2) - Working version
description:
As of today (March 14th, 2014), Popcorn Time decided to discontinue their project. The last update (Beta 2.5) doesn't work anymore, but for our luck, the old Beta 2 version is still working perfectly. 

As it may be hard to find, I decided to upload it here. 

We would all appreciate if programmers around the world decided to get this project back on track. Keep up the good work!
